257
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:06,200
Lynette?

258
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:11,200
Honey?
Are you home?

259
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,500
Three months?

260
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:17,000
God, you scared the hell out of me!

261
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,700
Were you ever going to tell me?

262
00:16:19,700 --> 00:16:22,800
