That's all.

274
00:16:56,900 --> 00:17:00,200
Well you can't work with her.
- What do you want me to do, quit?

275
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:02,600
Talk to Peterson. Maybe you can get a transfer.

276
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:05,500
Weren't you guys planning on
starting something up in Belize?

277
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,900
Honey, you're crazy!

278
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,400
No, I'm serious.

279
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:12,600
If she stays, I will haunt your office.

280
00:17:12,600 --> 00:17:14,900
I'll bring you lunch every day.

281
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:18,500
